TEMPLATE VAIRABLES

- get a typed value from input field.
- there are 2 ways:
- 1.
        <input (keyup.enter) = "onKeyUp($event)" />

        export class SomeClass(){
            //
            onKeyUp($event){
                console.log($event.target.value);
            }
        }


- 2.
        <input #email (keyup.enter) = onKeyUp(email.value) />

        export class SomeClass(){
            //
            onkeyUp(email){
                console.log(email);
            }
        }